Package io.zero88.jooqx

Class BindBatchValues

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.zero88.jooqx.BindBatchValues
  • public final class BindBatchValues
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a holder keep dummy value and list of binding records
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    JDBC batch operations, InsertSetStep.set(Map), UpdateSetStep.set(Map), MergeMatchedSetStep.set(Map)
    API Note:
    With dummy value records, you can predefine a field value, then if a bind record is missing this field value then system will auto detect and fallback to the predefined value. See: registerValue(Field, Object)
